							<div class="bg-black/60 px-3 py-2">
								<p class="text-white/80 text-xs leading-tight">Aná, Nodriza, Agua Sal o la Loca — nombres de la Quebrada Santa Elena</p>
								<p class="text-cyan-400/60 text-xs mt-1">Sandramirezgiraldo</p>
							</div>
						</a>

						<a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Cascada_Quebrada_Santa_Elena.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group block break-inside-avoid rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-cyan-500/20 hover:border-cyan-400/50 transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-cyan-900/40">
